<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Section_508_Amendment_to_the_Rehabilitation_Act_of_1973&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://html.cita.uiuc.edu" class="external text" title="http://html.cita.uiuc.edu" rel="nofollow">CITES/DRES Web Accessibility Best practices</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.access-board.gov/508.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.access-board.gov/508.htm" rel="nofollow">United States Access Board</a> the Federal Agency responsible for Section 508 technical standards</li>
<li><a href="http://www.webaim.org/standards/508/checklist" class="external text" title="http://www.webaim.org/standards/508/checklist" rel="nofollow">Section 508 Checklist</a> from WebAIM.org</li>
<li><a href="http://www.usps.com/cpim/ftp/hand/as508a/welcome.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.usps.com/cpim/ftp/hand/as508a/welcome.htm" rel="nofollow">USPS AS-508-A, <i>Section 508 Technical Reference Guide</i></a> in HTML Format</li>
<li><a href="http://www.usps.com/cpim/ftp/hand/as508a.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.usps.com/cpim/ftp/hand/as508a.pdf" rel="nofollow">USPS AS-508-A, <i>Section 508 Technical Reference Guide</i></a> in PDF Format</li>
<li><a href="http://www.access.gpo.gov/su_docs/fedreg/a001221c.html" class="external text" title="http://www.access.gpo.gov/su_docs/fedreg/a001221c.html" rel="nofollow">Federal Register December 2000</a> Section 508 Electronic and information technology accessibility standards</li>
<li><a href="http://www.access.gpo.gov/su_docs/fedreg/a010425c.html" class="external text" title="http://www.access.gpo.gov/su_docs/fedreg/a010425c.html" rel="nofollow">Federal Register April 2005</a> Section 508 related Federal Acquisition Rules</li>
<li><a href="http://www.itic.org/archives/articles/20040506/faq_voluntary_product_accessibility_templatetm_vpattm.php" class="external text" title="http://www.itic.org/archives/articles/20040506/faq_voluntary_product_accessibility_templatetm_vpattm.php" rel="nofollow">Voluntary Product Accessibility Template (VPAT)</a> Guidelines for using the VPAT.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.evengrounds.com/resources/vpat-directory" class="external text" title="http://www.evengrounds.com/resources/vpat-directory" rel="nofollow">Voluntary Product Accessibility Template (VPAT)</a> directory.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.section508.gov" class="external text" title="http://www.section508.gov" rel="nofollow">Section508.gov</a> - free 508 training.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.usability.gov" class="external text" title="http://www.usability.gov" rel="nofollow">Usability.gov</a> offers information on helping people with handicaps, includes a 508 compliance section.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.hhs.gov/web" class="external text" title="http://www.hhs.gov/web" rel="nofollow">Human Health and Services 508 compliance standards</a> for many government run sites.</li>
</ul>
