<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Section_508_Amendment_to_the_Rehabilitation_Act_of_1973&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10" title="Edit section: Free Accessibility Demonstrations &amp; Free Testing Sites">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Free Accessibility Demonstrations &amp; Free Testing Sites</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://fae.cita.uiuc.edu" class="external text" title="http://fae.cita.uiuc.edu" rel="nofollow">University of Illinois Functional Accessibility Evaluator</a> Free tool that creates summary web accessibility reports for administrators and detailed reports for developers</li>
<li><a href="http://firefox.cita.uiuc.edu" class="external text" title="http://firefox.cita.uiuc.edu" rel="nofollow">University of Illinois Firefox Accessibility Extension</a></li>
